Source: xlunch
Section: x11
Priority: optional
Maintainer: crims0n <crims0n@minios.dev>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 12), libimlib2-dev, libx11-dev
Standards-Version: 4.5.1
Homepage: https://github.com/Tomas-M/xlunch
Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: xlunch
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: Graphical application launcher for X using pure Xlib and Imlib2.
 Provides a lightweight, mouse- and keyboard-driven interface to launch
 programs, commands, or custom menu entries. Supports UTF-8 for international
 text and offers real-time filtering while typing. Highly configurable in both
 appearance and functionality, xlunch can even function as a minimal desktop
 environment.
